metadata.name: THE TEN #1
metadata.description:
Burnable NFT that gives you the ability to have Junior Jr. on your song in accordance with the terms and conditions: https://app.termly.io/document/terms-of-use-for-website/50bc304c-82ff-43bc-a8e4-7098fc7216e5

10  NFTs  - 10  Features  - 10  Absolute Bangers!!  This very well may be the first music NFT of its kind, and I hope it can be a step in the right direction for liberating independent music artists.
